      <h1><a href="/uncommon">Uncommon Sense</a></h1>
      <p class="postdate">Length: <strong>47 minutes.</strong> Date recorded: 2011-08</p>
    </header>
    <p><strong>All of my business advice for entrepreneurs. A quick summary of almost everything I’ve learned. One of my most popular talks.</strong></p>

<p>
This is the talk that a few different conferences paid the big bucks to have me do in-person.
But I don’t like repeating myself, so I hit record in the studio to share it for free.
</p><p>
It’s split into 8 parts, one subject each.
</p><p>
Click the “download” link to download an HD video to watch later.
Or just watch the streaming version here.
</p>
